Install
=======

First, to get the required options to work with the validations, you need to install validation_reflection plugin which add two methods reflect_on_all_validations and reflect_on_validations_for(:property) to the ActionRecord objects.

1. ruby script/plugin install git://github.com/redinger/validation_reflection.git


